==============================================================================
Files
==============================================================================

  1. printtrace.py - Read WiNS trace file and print formatted output.
  2. mergedata.py  - Merge multiple data sets together.
  3. plotdata.py   - Plot data points [with/without error bars].

==============================================================================
How to convert PDF to PNG
==============================================================================

Find out the dimensions using pdf info:

  > pdfinfo INPUT.PDF

Figure out the appropriate scaled size you want, and then convert the pdf:

  > convert -resize WIDTHxHEIGHT INPUT.PDF OUTPUT.PNG

